description: Efficient wire labeling with UCT-WMCO 6.8 (23x8). Easy-to-apply adhesive labels keep cables and circuits clearly identified. Durable, fade-resistant, and perfect for panels, workshops, and service vans—simplify cable management and maintenance.

Wire Marking Labels UCT-WMCO 4.7 (23x4). Compact, legible markers for fast wire identification. Strong adhesive, durable and weather-resistant, ideal for tight panels, telecom setups, and home installs. Keeps wiring organized and easy to troubleshoot.

Wire Marking Labels UCT-WMCO 7.5 (23x8). Large, clear markers for quick identification of multiple wires in panels and networks. Robust adhesive and long-lasting visibility; perfect for industrial, office, and home wiring projects.

Heat Shrink Tubing 6mm — protective insulation for wires. Shrinks to fit, seals moisture, and guards against abrasion. Easy to use with a heat source, making repairs and cable management neat and durable.
UTP Cat5e Ethernet Cable, 4-Pair, 305m. Reliable network cable for home and office. Flexible, easy to run, and ready for fast, stable connections across LAN and internet setups.
